content.body: I'd hoped to bring back extractors and void bindings for Stage 2 this plenary, but only recently had the time to address feedback from last meeting and I want to give Waldemar time to review the changes intended to address his concerns. I may try to add them as late agenda items since they both seemed fairly close to reaching stage 2 at the last meeting (or, at least that was my impression).
